pttnet¶

安裝¶

  • Python package (Python 3.7 )

    • pip3 install git+https://github.com/liao961120/ptt-network.git

    1. LOPE Drive Research/SemanticChange/ pttnet-data.zip
    2. cd pttnet-data
    3. pttnet_usage.ipynb ( data/ )

1. Network Structure¶

  • Node
    • Each node is a user (identified by ID)
    • Each node has a "corpus", consisting of comments
      • Comments are grouped under dates (yyyy-mm-dd)

  • Edge

    • If two user both left comments under a post, an edge is formed between them.

    • An edge is essentially a post and contains the following attributes (aside the nodes):

      {
      "title": "!!",
      "isRe": 0,
      "tag": "",
      "date": "2006-12-24",
      "board": "Boy-Girl",
      "opinion": "pos-pos",
      "text": "20061224_2348_M.1166975303.A.F56.json"
  }

2. High-level API: creating undirected graph¶

2.1 基本步驟¶

  1. MultiGraph() networkx.MultiGraph()

    • edge undirected & unweighted
    • node 1 edge

  2. Graph() MultiGraph()

    • node 1 edge
    • edge undirected & weighted

2.2 例子：以「使用者」為中心¶

2.2.1 建立 MultiGraph¶

2007 Boy-Girl airlow MultiGraph

In [1]:
import networkx as nx
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from pttnet.graph import MultiGraph, Graph

conditions = {
    'nodes': {'airlow'}
}
MG = MultiGraph(edge_condition=conditions, boards=['Boy-Girl'], years=[2007])
In [2]:
print(f"Num of nodes: {len(MG.nodes)}")
print(f"Num of edges: {len(MG.edges)}")

Num of nodes: 391
Num of edges: 1286
Node 物件¶

MG.nodes graph pttnet.graph.Node id corpus attributes

Node MG.nodes Nodes dictionary Node id

In [3]:
nodes = {n.id: n for n in MG.nodes}
nodes.get('airlow')
Out[3]:
<Node, node_id: airlow>

Node object Node.corpus attribute Boy-Girl12

1: Boy-Girl Node.corpus

MultiGraph()

In [13]:
conditions = {
    'title': {''},
    'tag': {''}
}
MG = MultiGraph(edge_condition=conditions, boards=['Boy-Girl'], years=[2007])

print(f"Num of nodes: {len(MG.nodes)}")
print(f"Num of edges: {len(MG.edges)}")

Num of edges: 2287

posts = {}
for n1, n2, data in edges:
    id_ = data['text']
    if id_ not in posts:
        posts[id_] = 1
    else:
        posts[id_] += 1

posts
